name: Circus clown
description: The image of the clown is always weird and funny, and the clown facing the audience is always a smiling face. So we have an inherent impression of clowns-clowns always love to laugh.But in fact, many clowns' makeup will deliberately put tears on the corners of their eyes, which is in sharp contrast with the laughing red lip makeup. This makes people wonder whether clowns love to laugh or cry?
